-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Extensions
A simple annotations based extensions framework.

Preferences
Global preferences with built in class hierarchy searching.

Reflections
Interface to org.reflections classpath scanner.

Examples
Examples of how to use the Cadian framework.

  NinjaBattle
  An example showing how cadian-extensions allows you to create and classify multiple hierarchies of extensions.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install
In cadian-reflections
  $ mvn install
In cadian-properties
  $ mvn install
In cadian-extensions
  $ mvn install
In cadian-examples
  $ mvn install

Run the NinjaBattle example
In cadian-examples
  $ mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="org.cadian.examples.extensions.ninjabattle.NinjaBattle"
